data.description:
This is the one! Welcome to Leisure Knoll, a gated community in Manchester. This Danbury model has been updated to include: BRAND NEW ROOF, NEW HEAT AND AC, CONVERTED TO NATURAL GAS, sprinkler system, recessed lighting,  luxury vinyl plank flooring, new bathrooms and kitchen.  
As you enter into the home you will see the spacious floor plan. The living room, dining area, den and kitchen have 5 inch crown molding.
Make your appointment to see this gem soon!
*some photos are virtually staged, grass enhanced
